'''Qoys''' ({{lang-ar|أسرة}} {{lang-it|famiglia}} {{lang-en|family}}) waa dad ka kooban dhowr qof, ugu yaraan labo qof ([[seey]] iyo [[xaas]]), kuwaas oo hal aqal wada degan. Qoysku waa [[waalid]] ([[hooyo]] iyo [[aabo]]), [[aboowe]] iyo [[abaayo]] ([[ubad]]ka), [[ilmo|ilmaha]], [[ciyaal]]ka, [[caruur]]ta iyo dad [[qaraabo]] ah oo hal meel ku wada nool. 
